Keep in mind that the `font-weight` property only accepts specific values like `'normal'`, `'bold'`, `'bolder'`, or a number between 100 and 900 corresponding to the desired weight. 

You can use this approach to add any CSS property to your components using inline styles. Simply define an object literal containing the CSS properties you want to apply and pass it as a prop to your component's `style` attribute.

